===Foreign non-state decorations===
* Gold Collar of the [[Olympic Order]] ([[International Olympic Committee]], 1984), for decision not to participate in the boycott of the [[1984 Summer Olympics|Los Angeles Olympics]]
* Gold Medal Plate of the [[Istituto Affari Internazionali|International Relations Institute of Rome]], an Italian non-profit organization (1979)

===Academic titles===
Honorary degrees from the [[University of Bucharest]] (1973), [[Lebanese University]] (1974), [[University of Buenos Aires]] (1974), [[Autonomous University of Yucatan]] (1975), [[University of Nice Sophia Antipolis]] (1975), [[University of the Philippines]] (1975), [[University of Liberia]] (1988) and [[North Korea]] (1988).

